### Welcome to My project ### Hi there,

This is my first git hub project ever started and truly excited !

Well, I wanted to start by coding basic data structures in C. So i have uploaded single linked list program. Please download them and refer to README to see how to build and yes! enjoy running my executable :-). I will be happy to receive valid suggestions from you. ### Authors and Contributors Suresh Janipalli (@janipallisuresh).
